don bosco institute of technology (dbit) is a technological and science education college located in kumbalagodu village, bangalore. in 2001, don bosco institute of technology, was established on a rambling sylvan area of about 36 acres (15 ha) campus, about 6 kilometres (3.7 mi) away from kengeri bordering the bangaloreâ€“mysore road. dbit provides civil, mechanical, engineering technology, computer and management education.